    "description": {
      "value": "The cards of this deck shimmer around the edges. While holding this deck, you can use the following properties:\n\n- Deadly Deal: As an action, you can use this deck to make a ranged spell attack by throwing a spectral card and using Dexterity for the attack roll. The card has a range of 120 feet and deals 1d8 force damage on a hit.\n- Spray of Cards: As an action, you can shuffle the deck and cast the Spray of Cards spell at 3rd level from the deck (spell save DC 15). Once the deck has cast the spell, it can't cast the spell again until the next dawn."
    },
